module.exports = /*#__PURE__*/JSON.parse('[{"id":"module_1","title":"Who is God? (The Trinity)","theme":"God is a Loving Family","targetAge":"Ages 3+","talkingPoints":["God is a Father: He is completely safe. He is never moody or waiting to get angry. He is always bursting with love for us.","Jesus shows us God: If we want to know what God looks like, we look at Jesus. Jesus is kind, strong, and heals people.","The Holy Spirit is our Helper: God\'s love isn\'t far away; He puts His Spirit right inside our hearts to give us \'God-hugs\' from the inside."]},{"id":"module_2","title":"The Good World & The Sickness","theme":"Creation and the Fall","targetAge":"Ages 3+","talkingPoints":["God makes beautiful things: The trees, animals, and people were all made because God wanted to share His love.","The Big Owie: People decided they didn\'t want to stay close to God\'s light. When they walked away, the world got a \'big owie\' (sin). People started getting sad and sick.","God didn\'t run away: When we get an owie, God doesn\'t get mad at us for bleeding. He immediately promises to come fix it."]},{"id":"module_3","title":"The Great Rescue","theme":"Christus Victor & The Physician","targetAge":"Ages 3+","talkingPoints":["The Brave Doctor: Jesus came into our broken world to be our Doctor. He took our \'big owie\' on Himself on the cross to make the medicine we need.","Beating the Dark: Jesus went into the darkest cave where death hides. Because He is the strongest King, He broke the doors, woke up, and chased the scary things away!","The Empty Tomb: Easter is the best surprise party ever because Jesus won, and now He shares His life with us."]},{"id":"module_4","title":"The Reign of Grace","theme":"Freedom from Fear","targetAge":"Ages 4+","talkingPoints":["Grace means \'Free Gift\': We can never earn God\'s love, and we can never lose it. It is entirely free.","Running to the Light: When we make a mistake, we don\'t hide. We run straight to Jesus. Saying \'I\'m sorry\' is just letting the Doctor put a band-aid on our heart.","Living by the Spirit: We don\'t have to carry a heavy backpack of rules. The Holy Spirit gives us the power to be kind and brave."]},{"id":"module_5","title":"Spiritual Reality","theme":"Light vs. Dark","targetAge":"Ages 4+","talkingPoints":["Two Teams: There is a real invisible world. God\'s team is light and life. The enemy\'s team is dark and tricky, trying to make people forget God\'s love.","Total Victory: The bad guys already lost on Easter. They have no real power over us. Their only weapon is telling lies.","Armor of Light: Because Jesus is in us, we are filled with light. We never have to be scared of the dark, bad dreams, or anything unseen."]}]');

